{"_id":"28729dfcf80d4d76b98be4feae9d016e","uid":"fca812f055d5fdcd3a355b63ceaad991","nick":"lvbibir","mail":"15810243114@163.com","mailMd5":"081f5d4eddf093b6bc2ca2cd4ae5d188","link":"https://www.lvbibir.cn","ua":"Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/108.0.0.0 Safari/537.36","ip":"111.203.234.211","master":true,"url":"/links/","href":"https://www.lvbibir.cn/links/","comment":"<ol>\n<li><p>下载字体文件上传到你的服务器或者存储(<a href=\"https://image.lvbibir.cn/fonts/%E6%B1%89%E4%BB%AA%E5%8A%B2%E6%A5%B7%E7%AE%80.woff2\">https://image.lvbibir.cn/fonts/%E6%B1%89%E4%BB%AA%E5%8A%B2%E6%A5%B7%E7%AE%80.woff2</a>)</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>在font.css中定义 @font-face</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<pre><code class=\"language-css\">@font-face {\n    font-family: \"han-yi-jin-kai-jian\";\n    src: url(\"字体文件，本地路径或者网络路径\") format(\"truetype\");\n    font-display: swap;\n}\n</code></pre>\n<ol start=\"3\">\n<li>在你的CSS中定义 font-family，比如</li>\n</ol>\n<pre><code class=\"language-css\">.post-content {\n    font-family: \"han-yi-jin-kai-jian\";\n}\n</code></pre>\n","pid":"c498230454a3410e8ab8b3cc57f728e2","rid":"c498230454a3410e8ab8b3cc57f728e2","created":1673252186984,"updated":1673252186984,"meta":{"revision":0,"created":1673252186996,"version":0},"$loki":23,"id":"28729dfcf80d4d76b98be4feae9d016e","ipRegion":"北京 北京市 联通"}
