{"_id":"da1f1d657eb745c5b023bc7a6e592807","uid":"e9ea9f03fdd4439296c696cb949287f4","nick":"必填","mail":"charle00001@proton.me","mailMd5":"031297045d8341ef0b9ea97c6d354f2c","link":"charle00001.github.io","ua":"Mozilla/5.0 (Macintosh; Intel Mac OS X 10.15; rv:109.0) Gecko/20100101 Firefox/115.0","ip":"83.233.246.72","master":false,"url":"/posts/blog/hello-hugo/","href":"https://www.lvbibir.cn/posts/blog/hello-hugo/#%e6%9b%b4%e6%96%b0","comment":"<p>终于葱hexo迁移到hugo了<br>在这里不得不吐槽一下hexo<br>太折腾了，乱七八糟的配置文件把我搞得眼花缭乱<br>虽然hugo也有折腾的空间，但是至少没有像hexo那样长的“主题配置文件”！！！<br>而且感觉nodejs的生成速度也不尽如人意<br>关键是上次我把博客的主题改成了butterfly，一打开自己的博客我的2017年的macbookair的cpu立马狂转<br>我玩mc我的cpu都没有这么转过<br>再次吐槽hexo和nodejs<br>=）</p>\n","created":1699713818193,"updated":1699713818193,"meta":{"revision":0,"created":1699713818208,"version":0},"$loki":53,"id":"da1f1d657eb745c5b023bc7a6e592807","ipRegion":"0 0"}
{"_id":"5de667371d2c49cc8e6ff4ed7789171d","uid":"fca812f055d5fdcd3a355b63ceaad991","nick":"lvbibir","mail":"15810243114@163.com","mailMd5":"081f5d4eddf093b6bc2ca2cd4ae5d188","link":"https://www.lvbibir.cn","ua":"Mozilla/5.0 (Linux; Android 11; Pixel 5) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/90.0.4430.91 Mobile Safari/537.36","ip":"124.127.221.86","master":true,"url":"/posts/blog/hello-hugo/","href":"https://www.lvbibir.cn/posts/blog/hello-hugo/#da1f1d657eb745c5b023bc7a6e592807","comment":"<p>但是 hexo 用的人确实多，hugo 很多地方要翻官方的英文文档，主题数量也挺让人羡慕的</p>\n","pid":"da1f1d657eb745c5b023bc7a6e592807","rid":"da1f1d657eb745c5b023bc7a6e592807","created":1700029407067,"updated":1700029407067,"meta":{"revision":0,"created":1700029407075,"version":0},"$loki":54,"id":"5de667371d2c49cc8e6ff4ed7789171d","ipRegion":"北京 北京市 电信"}
