{"_id":"6f918276d9ce46d8b9516fdeddfd3c8c","uid":"fca812f055d5fdcd3a355b63ceaad991","nick":"lvbibir","mail":"15810243114@163.com","mailMd5":"081f5d4eddf093b6bc2ca2cd4ae5d188","link":"15810243114@163.com","ua":"Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/119.0.0.0 Safari/537.36","ip":"115.171.166.142","master":true,"url":"/posts/blog/hello-hugo/","href":"https://www.lvbibir.cn/posts/blog/hello-hugo/","comment":"<p>目前工作用邮箱很少, 所以不怎么看邮件, 所以回复会比较随缘</p>\n","pid":"3c7767a5bbfd45e4b352d33d3831008f","rid":"3c7767a5bbfd45e4b352d33d3831008f","created":1700738658633,"updated":1700738658633,"meta":{"revision":0,"created":1700738658635,"version":0},"$loki":57,"id":"6f918276d9ce46d8b9516fdeddfd3c8c","ipRegion":"北京 北京市 电信"}
{"_id":"6c9a751e483a493784d29b52e57d51a3","uid":"fca812f055d5fdcd3a355b63ceaad991","nick":"lvbibir","mail":"15810243114@163.com","mailMd5":"081f5d4eddf093b6bc2ca2cd4ae5d188","link":"15810243114@163.com","ua":"Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/119.0.0.0 Safari/537.36","ip":"115.171.166.142","master":true,"url":"/posts/blog/hello-hugo/","href":"https://www.lvbibir.cn/posts/blog/hello-hugo/","comment":"<p>能识别到系统版本和浏览器版本, 识别不到 IP</p>\n","pid":"3c7767a5bbfd45e4b352d33d3831008f","rid":"3c7767a5bbfd45e4b352d33d3831008f","created":1700738685657,"updated":1700738685657,"meta":{"revision":0,"created":1700738685659,"version":0},"$loki":58,"id":"6c9a751e483a493784d29b52e57d51a3","ipRegion":"北京 北京市 电信"}
{"_id":"6b62b0035c884f99b58383bf25a69dd5","uid":"b01222d58f114ba4b89a64e1961fc3cc","nick":"必填","mail":"charle00001@proton.me","mailMd5":"031297045d8341ef0b9ea97c6d354f2c","link":"https://charle00001.github.io/","ua":"Mozilla/5.0 (X11; CrOS x86_64 14541.0.0) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/119.0.0.0 Safari/537.36","ip":"193.180.104.60","master":false,"url":"/posts/blog/hello-hugo/","href":"https://www.lvbibir.cn/posts/blog/hello-hugo/#6c9a751e483a493784d29b52e57d51a3","comment":"<p>我把評論系統换到waline之后也没什么太大的感觉，之前尝试了disqus、valine、livere（来必力），不想再折腾了。直接waline走起，<br>但是坏处是部署在vercel、leancloud国际版上，要冒着”非法连接国际互联网”的这种【大罪】来评论。<br>之前用过valine，但是后来爆出了【安全性问题】停止使用<br>那些由”大公司平台”实现的（disqus等等）就不考虑了<br>当然自己搭建的waline总归没那么稳定<br>但是懒得折腾了<br>当然vercel无法访问的问题其实可以搞一台vps直接反代，甚至直接搭在vps上，但是懒死了就算了吧<br><br><br>不过话说我昨天发现我那远在<del>天朝</del>中国的【朋友兼同学】的那家伙居然没有学会”网民上网的基本技能”（更科学的使用互联网），就只能含泪帮他下载小火箭、电报，还送他了俩节点<br>只能这样帮他了。。。。。。<br>o(<em>////▽////</em>)q </p>\n","created":1701938184141,"updated":1701938184141,"meta":{"revision":0,"created":1701938184147,"version":0},"$loki":61,"id":"6b62b0035c884f99b58383bf25a69dd5","ipRegion":"0 0"}
{"_id":"63869cd6bee44fa1a6bffbaec89c5893","uid":"b01222d58f114ba4b89a64e1961fc3cc","nick":"必填","mail":"charle00001@proton.me","mailMd5":"031297045d8341ef0b9ea97c6d354f2c","link":"https://charle00001.github.io/","ua":"Mozilla/5.0 (X11; CrOS x86_64 14541.0.0) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/119.0.0.0 Safari/537.36","ip":"193.180.104.60","master":false,"url":"/posts/blog/hello-hugo/","href":"https://www.lvbibir.cn/posts/blog/hello-hugo/#6c9a751e483a493784d29b52e57d51a3","comment":"<p>p.s.<br>我现在在用我的学校电脑进行评论，所以显示chromeos<br>(๑•̀ㅁ•́ฅ)</p>\n","pid":"6b62b0035c884f99b58383bf25a69dd5","rid":"6b62b0035c884f99b58383bf25a69dd5","created":1701938376976,"updated":1701938376976,"meta":{"revision":0,"created":1701938376978,"version":0},"$loki":62,"id":"63869cd6bee44fa1a6bffbaec89c5893","ipRegion":"0 0"}
