{"_id":"ad17be14bd4d4983b77ca66bc2f5634a","uid":"d856d8dbeef340ce9ae16cfb4bd0665f","nick":"和嘿嘿","mail":"1365253129@qq.com","mailMd5":"1d8652136344122d87826871c078dd17","link":"","ua":"Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/121.0.0.0 Safari/537.36 Edg/121.0.0.0","ip":"182.203.75.50","master":false,"url":"/posts/tech/windows-early-auto-start/","href":"https://www.lvbibir.cn/posts/tech/windows-early-auto-start/","comment":"<p>你好  我按照你的方法试了 重启 开机 没效果  我只有注销进来才有用 win11系统、</p>\n","created":1706410449401,"updated":1706410449401,"avatar":null,"meta":{"revision":0,"created":1706410449476,"version":0},"$loki":71,"id":"ad17be14bd4d4983b77ca66bc2f5634a","ipRegion":"辽宁省 营口市 电信"}
{"_id":"d792b9bc31f942c3bb9f93bd327d09f5","uid":"fca812f055d5fdcd3a355b63ceaad991","nick":"lvbibir","mail":"15810243114@163.com","mailMd5":"081f5d4eddf093b6bc2ca2cd4ae5d188","link":"15810243114@163.com","ua":"Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/120.0.0.0 Safari/537.36","ip":"124.126.183.252","master":true,"url":"/posts/tech/windows-early-auto-start/","href":"https://www.lvbibir.cn/posts/tech/windows-early-auto-start/","comment":"<p>我是 win10, 这个项目很久没更新了, 挺大可能不适配 win11 的.<br>也有 win11 用户配置成功了, 可以看下我 <a href=\"https://cloud.tencent.com/developer/article/2345804\">腾讯云社区文章</a> 的评论, 可以回评论问一下</p>\n","pid":"ad17be14bd4d4983b77ca66bc2f5634a","rid":"ad17be14bd4d4983b77ca66bc2f5634a","created":1706411553304,"updated":1706411553304,"meta":{"revision":0,"created":1706411553310,"version":0},"$loki":72,"id":"d792b9bc31f942c3bb9f93bd327d09f5","ipRegion":"北京 北京市 电信"}
{"_id":"40e83fa42df74fa99ba830cca1d4e58c","uid":"567008ac053048118257f3c3cb043f4c","nick":"1411652956@qq.com","mail":"1411652956@qq.com","mailMd5":"4c7c1c6f8cf6434f91283dce26e1ad48","link":"","ua":"Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/121.0.0.0 Safari/537.36 Edg/121.0.0.0","ip":"116.224.117.207","master":false,"url":"/posts/tech/pxe-dhcp-legacy-uefi-archs/","href":"https://www.lvbibir.cn/posts/tech/pxe-dhcp-legacy-uefi-archs/#1-rfc","comment":"<p>感谢  学习了</p>\n","created":1706594709815,"updated":1706594709815,"avatar":null,"meta":{"revision":0,"created":1706594709877,"version":0},"$loki":73,"id":"40e83fa42df74fa99ba830cca1d4e58c"}
{"_id":"d79d4d9c60134f83886e1a71777ffceb","uid":"9fbcdd9da7f94939bade85ff4b56d496","nick":"折翼纸鹤","mail":"admin@itcent.cn","mailMd5":"2ff65ade5fee188e5d2b6935ac899c89","link":"www.itcent.cn","ua":"Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/120.0.0.0 Safari/537.36 Edg/120.0.0.0","ip":"125.33.196.51","master":false,"url":"/posts/tech/pxe-dhcp-legacy-uefi-archs/","href":"https://www.lvbibir.cn/posts/tech/pxe-dhcp-legacy-uefi-archs/#2-dhcp-option-60","comment":"<p>非常不错，之前一直只会使用模板来回切换，一直想学怎么抓包自己配置，终于找到有用的文章了。<br>但是我还有个问题，就是使用dhcpd服务都可以配置，正常使用。（dhcpd+dnsmasq+tftpserver+httpd）<br>现在想只使用dnsmasq+http服务实现，在dnsmasq中，dhcp-boot功能很多转化不了语句，按照网上查找的配置就错误，服务启动失败。目前只能实现dhcp-boot=undionly.kpxe或dhcp-boot=ipxe.efi单条参数控制。</p>\n<p>我尝试加入dhcp-boot=arch:00:00,undionly.kpxe,虽然服务可以正常启动，但是客户端并不能获取undionly.kpxe</p>\n","created":1709716929171,"updated":1709716929171,"meta":{"revision":1,"created":1709716929175,"version":0,"updated":1709789551474},"$loki":74,"id":"d79d4d9c60134f83886e1a71777ffceb","like":["9fbcdd9da7f94939bade85ff4b56d496"]}
